{"id":1095,"title":"Effect of aging on cardiac function plus monitoring and support.","abstract":"Cardiovascular disease is the most prevalent and influential comorbidity affecting outcomes in geriatric surgical patients. The unique physiology of the aging cardiovascular system and the impact of these changes during the stress of surgery is presented in this article. The necessary response to these changes is discussed with attention to methods of monitoring and recommendations for providing supportive care. ","date":"2014-12-03","categories":"Cardiovascular Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25459540","annotations":[{"name":"Cardiovascular disease","weight":0.87818,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardiovascular_disease"},{"name":"Stress (biology)","weight":0.836829,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stress_(biology)"},{"name":"Physiology","weight":0.787886,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physiology"},{"name":"Ageing","weight":0.784197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ageing"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.781843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Heart","weight":0.71741,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heart"},{"name":"Cardiovascular system","weight":0.711738,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardiovascular_system"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.684152,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Circulatory system","weight":0.684152,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circulatory_system"},{"name":"Geriatrics","weight":0.637578,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geriatrics"},{"name":"Comorbidity","weight":0.546188,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comorbidity"},{"name":"Cardiology diagnostic tests and procedures","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardiology_diagnostic_tests_and_procedures"}]}
